05:03.380 --> 05:07.176
<i>that final upheaval of the world
foretold by the prophets of old.</i>

05:07.259 --> 05:11.680
<i>But amid all the pessimism, one voice
rings out its faith in the future:</i>

05:11.763 --> 05:16.351
<i>Thorn, the world's leading light
