Do we have footage of the
Australian drought relief?

05:56.725 --> 06:01.313
Sure, but nothing new, and most
of it's been seen on TV already.

06:02.523 --> 06:06.735
We'll find you something. In the
meantime, go with the old commercial.

06:06.819 --> 06:09.530
I don't want that one used.

06:10.989 --> 06:15.244
- What have we got coming up?
- Botswana next week, then the Aswan Dam.

06:15.327 --> 06:17.265
Can we get a film
unit to Botswana?

06:17.266 --> 06:19.957
Sure, but no relief unit
till after the coup.

06:20.040 --> 06:22.481
No one's sure how long
that's gonna take.

06:22.482 --> 06:25.212
All right. It'll have
to be the Aswan Dam.

06:25.295 --> 06:27.923
Have a film unit there
when it goes. Make

06:27.924 --> 06:30.551
sure they give our
relief units coverage.

06:30.634 --> 06:33.720
Don't let the Red Cross
beat them to it.

06:33.804 --> 06:36.473
Why don't <i>you</i> go? Now that
would be a real coup.

06:36.557 --> 06:40.811
Damien Thorn supervising
relief work in person!

06:40.894 --> 06:43.313
No, I've got to stay here.

06:43.397 --> 06:47.234
- What for?
- To be on hand when the president calls me.

06:49.319 --> 06:54.324
He's, uh, gonna offer me the post
of ambassador to Great Britain.

06:54.408 --> 06:58.453
- I beg your pardon?
- Are you familiar with the Book of Hebron?

06:58.537 --> 07:02.541
No, I don't know anything
about the Book of Hebron.

07:02.624 --> 07:05.842
It's in the Apocrypha.
One of the more

07:05.843 --> 07:09.381
obscure backwaters of
the Septuagint Bible.

07:11.175 --> 07:14.303
"And it shall come to pass
that in the end days...

07:14.386 --> 07:19.266
the beast shall reign one hundred
score and thirty days and nights."

07:19.349 --> 07:23.437
"And the faithful shall
cry unto the Lord:

07:23.520 --> 07:26.857
Wherefore art thou
in the day of evil?"

07:26.940 --> 07:30.152
"And the Lord shall
hear their prayers."

07:30.235 --> 07:34.364
"And out of the angel isle he
shall bring forth a deliverer..."

07:34.448 --> 07:39.161
a holy lamb of God who shall
do battle with the beast...

07:40.787 --> 07:43.457
"and shall destroy him."

07:44.708 --> 07:48.754
"The beast shall reign one hundred
score and thirty days and nights"...

07:48.837 --> 07:51.590
is another way of
saying seven years.

07:51.673 --> 07:54.676
That's the time I've
been head of Thorn.

07:54.760 --> 07:58.514
"And out of the angel isle he
shall bring forth a deliverer."

07:58.597 --> 08:03.227
The "angel isle" - the original
Latin has <i>"ex insula angelorum".</i>

08:04.019 --> 08:06.230
England.

08:06.313 --> 08:08.106
The Second Coming.

08:08.273 --> 08:11.777
Only it won't be the
beast that is destroyed.

08:14.947 --> 08:16.740
It'll be the Nazarene.

08:16.824 --> 08:18.852
Damien, you said you
were gonna be offered

08:18.853 --> 08:20.786
the post of ambassador
to Great Britain.

08:20.869 --> 08:23.831
What about our
present ambassador?

10:38.257 --> 10:40.342
Afternoon, sir.

10:49.268 --> 10:51.478
Good afternoon, Mr. Ambassador.

10:51.562 --> 10:55.482
Good afternoon, Mr. Ambassador. I
just had Mr. Sears on the line.

10:55.566 --> 10:59.486
- No calls from anyone.
- He said it was urgent and I was to remind...

11:41.612 --> 11:44.239
- Press office.
<i>- This is the ambassador.</i>

11:44.323 --> 11:46.909
<i>I want a press conference.
Three o'clock.</i>

13:24.256 --> 13:26.133
Come in.

13:36.351 --> 13:38.270
Oh, my God!

13:46.236 --> 13:48.322
I know that.

13:49.198 --> 13:53.285
No. I'm not giving out any statements
- to him or to anyone else.

13:53.368 --> 13:56.163
It'll only make matters worse.

13:56.246 --> 13:59.958
Make sure that the cable
is non-committal as well.

14:00.292 --> 14:01.960
Yeah.

14:02.044 --> 14:04.755
Let me see it
before you send it.

14:07.800 --> 14:10.260
Gee. Can you believe that?

14:12.554 --> 14:15.891
Some sons of bitches from the
Egyptian opposition party...

14:15.974 --> 14:21.563
want us to endorse their condemnation
of Israel for blowing up the Aswan Dam.

14:21.647 --> 14:24.316
How the hell do <i>we</i> know
Israel's responsible?

14:24.399 --> 14:27.653
- My guess is it's the work of the NLF.
- Who?

14:27.736 --> 14:30.906
The Nubian Liberation Front
- a quasi-Marxist outfit.

14:30.989 --> 14:33.170
They've had a gripe
against Cairo since the

14:33.171 --> 14:35.202
'60s, when the High
Aswan Dam was built.

14:35.285 --> 14:37.803
They claim that it
submerged 50 per cent of

14:37.804 --> 14:40.207
their homeland, which,
of course, it did.

14:40.290 --> 14:42.376
Until now.

14:43.669 --> 14:46.088
How'd you get this information?

14:46.171 --> 14:50.884
One of our Thorn relief teams - they were
on the scene ahead of the Egyptians.

14:51.552 --> 14:53.887
I wanna take a look at that.

14:53.971 --> 14:57.141
It's quite, uh,
unofficial, of course.

14:57.975 --> 15:01.137
I don't have to point out
to you that... if we

15:01.138 --> 15:04.231
can prove it had nothing
to do with Israel...

15:04.314 --> 15:08.026
we could be averting one
mother of a major flare-up.

15:08.110 --> 15:11.473
I'll have to check it
myself. I wouldn't want

15:11.474 --> 15:14.616
to feed the White House
false information.

15:15.659 --> 15:18.245
As to the other matter...

15:18.328 --> 15:21.331
I'm afraid I can't
accept the post.

15:21.415 --> 15:24.031
If I were ambassador
to Great Britain, I'd

15:24.032 --> 15:26.587
have to relinquish my
control over Thorn.

15:26.670 --> 15:30.132
Hell, no! We can take
care of that for you.

15:30.674 --> 15:35.846
- It <i>is</i> against the law.
- Then we'll just have to bend it a little.

15:35.929 --> 15:39.224
But there are two
other conditions.

15:39.308 --> 15:41.393
What?

15:42.478 --> 15:44.563
Well, first...

15:45.355 --> 15:51.236
it could only be for two years, because
of running for the Senate in '84.

15:51.320 --> 15:55.073
And second, I'd want the
presidency of the Youth Council.

15:57.034 --> 16:01.497
- I've already promised that to Foster.
- I realize it's a problem.

16:19.515 --> 16:22.100
The NI... what?

16:22.184 --> 16:24.895
The Nubian Liberation Front.

16:32.694 --> 16:34.780
- Craig.
<i>- Yes, Mr. President.</i>

16:35.706 --> 16:38.292
I've just appointed Mr.
Damien Thorn as our

16:38.293 --> 16:40.702
new ambassador to the
Court of St James.

16:40.786 --> 16:43.831
Have Eisenberg prepare a press
release to that effect.

16:43.914 --> 16:46.208
<i>Right away, Mr. President.</i>

16:55.300 --> 16:57.594
- Craig.
<i>- Yes, Mr. President.</i>

16:59.513 --> 17:02.766
Add to that that I've also
appointed Mr. Thorn...

17:02.850 --> 17:07.563
as president of the United
Nations Youth Council.

17:07.646 --> 17:11.275
<i>- But I thought...</i>
- Just do it... will you?

17:17.906 --> 17:20.200
Well, Damien...

17:20.284 --> 17:23.829
your father would have
been very proud of you.

17:26.248 --> 17:28.625
I appreciate your
sentiments, sir.

17:33.046 --> 17:37.968
Cassiopeia. Right ascension.
One hour, 16 minutes, 12.

17:38.051 --> 17:41.013
Select declination
at 22 degrees...

17:41.096 --> 17:43.307
on an eight-by-four ratio.

17:43.390 --> 17:47.060
Super grid R-3 at
eight diagonal.

17:47.144 --> 17:50.939
- Eight diagonal.
- Increase focal length to max.

17:52.900 --> 17:56.403
- Hold. OK, Tony. Hard copy.
- Right.

