And... December 1928.

18:38.070 --> 18:42.574
- Well, what would <i>you</i> say?
- I'd say I was dreaming.

18:42.658 --> 18:47.204
- And the rate of acceleration?
- A couple of thousand parsecs, minimum!

18:47.287 --> 18:50.035
I'd say we're in for
one hell of a bang.

18:50.036 --> 18:52.918
Oh, no. An alignment,
not a collision.

18:53.001 --> 18:57.756
Let's transfer to the simulator, see if we
can't get an accurate schedule predict.

18:57.840 --> 18:59.925
Right.

19:02.803 --> 19:05.305
Whenever you're ready.

19:38.922 --> 19:42.384
<i>Verbo sanctificatur omnia...</i>

19:42.468 --> 19:46.763
<i>benedictionem tuam effunde
super scuti istas.</i>

19:47.473 --> 19:49.683
<i>Per Christum dominum nostrum.</i>

19:50.184 --> 19:52.269
<i>Amen.</i>

19:58.108 --> 20:00.444
Oh, blessed Saviour...

20:00.527 --> 20:03.197
who hath, through
the confession...

20:03.280 --> 20:06.950
of thy departed servant
Father Spiletto...

20:07.034 --> 20:12.748
revealed unto us the identity of
the Antichrist here on earth.

20:13.081 --> 20:16.752
Grant us thy strength
and guidance...

20:16.835 --> 20:19.421
in our holy mission...

20:19.505 --> 20:23.509
that we may rid the world
of Damien Thorn...

20:23.592 --> 20:28.722
and thus ensure the safety
of thy Second Coming.

20:30.390 --> 20:32.392
Oh, Lord...

20:32.476 --> 20:37.231
bless these seven sacred
knives from Megiddo...

20:37.314 --> 20:42.903
which thou hast seen fit
to return unto us...

20:42.986 --> 20:46.907
that they may serve
their holy purpose...

20:47.324 --> 20:51.662
and destroy the
Prince of Darkness...

20:51.745 --> 20:57.209
even as he seeketh to
destroy thy child of light.

21:06.718 --> 21:10.722
I now call upon each of
you to come forward...

21:10.806 --> 21:14.518
and arm yourselves in
the name of the Lord.

21:15.519 --> 21:17.604
Brother Martin.

21:22.734 --> 21:24.820
Brother Paulo.

21:32.452 --> 21:37.708
Each of us must pray to our Lord
in the silence of his own soul.

21:37.791 --> 21:42.838
Since we are prepared to lay down our lives
in the pursuit of this enterprise...

21:42.921 --> 21:47.301
we must seek final
absolution from God now...

21:47.384 --> 21:51.805
lest we be denied the redemption
of the blessed last sacrament...

21:51.889 --> 21:53.974
at the moment of death.

21:54.057 --> 22:00.314
Above all, we must ask God to grant
us courage, guidance and strength...

22:00.397 --> 22:05.861
as we prepare to do battle with
Satan and his son, the Antichrist.

22:05.944 --> 22:12.409
The exact hour of our Lord's Second
Coming, for which centuries have wept...

22:12.493 --> 22:16.872
has now been revealed to us
by signs in the heavens.

22:16.955 --> 22:22.836
It is imperative that the destruction of
the Antichrist takes place before then...

22:22.920 --> 22:26.423
and we have but a short time
in which to carry it out.

22:27.299 --> 22:33.013
My brothers, remember that these
seven daggers and ourselves...

22:33.096 --> 22:37.810
are all that stand between the son
of Satan and the Son of God...

22:37.893 --> 22:40.103
for they alone can destroy him.

22:50.197 --> 22:52.950
- Can't quite place it, can you?
- No.

22:54.034 --> 22:56.806
Waiter, let me have a
look at the label on

22:56.807 --> 22:59.706
the bottle of wine we're
drinking, will you?

23:08.382 --> 23:10.551
Is he really only 32?

23:10.634 --> 23:15.180
No idea. Shouldn't be surprised.
Americans always seem to think...

23:15.264 --> 23:19.643
they can run before they can
walk. Like their wine, what?

23:20.853 --> 23:25.274
The answer is yes. He's the youngest
ambassador ever appointed by the president.

23:25.357 --> 23:29.278
- Are you part of his staff?
- I'm his private secretary, Harvey Dean.

23:29.361 --> 23:32.197
- Kate Reynolds, British television.
- My wife Barbara.

23:32.281 --> 23:34.366
- How do you do?
- We're fine.

23:35.784 --> 23:38.871
- Lafite-Thorn.
- Must have bought the bugger out!

23:38.954 --> 23:43.584
Mm. Amazing what they can make
with soya beans these days.

23:43.667 --> 23:48.130
- Would you like to meet the ambassador?
- Oh, yes. Yes, I would. Thank you.

23:48.213 --> 23:50.299
Be back in a jiffy.

23:50.841 --> 23:52.843
- Good evening, Mrs. Dean.
- Hello.

23:52.926 --> 23:55.971
- When is the happy event?
- Next week, I hope.

23:57.598 --> 24:01.018
Damien. I'd like you
to meet Kate Reynolds.

24:01.019 --> 24:04.438
Miss Reynolds works for
British television.

24:04.771 --> 24:09.943
She has her own weekly news show.
It's called <i>The World in Vision.</i>

24:10.027 --> 24:13.405
<i>- In Focus.</i>
- Oh, excuse me. <i>The World in Focus.</i>

24:13.489 --> 24:16.700
Or out of focus, as
the case may be.

24:17.159 --> 24:22.498
How do you do, Miss Reynolds? The
Barbara Walters of British television?

24:22.581 --> 24:26.919
On my salary? They don't call us the British
Broadcasting Charity for nothing(!)

24:27.002 --> 24:29.719
Well, that makes two of
us. I'm in the charity

24:29.720 --> 24:32.090
business as well. What
can I do for you?

24:32.174 --> 24:36.512
Actually, I'd like to talk about doing
an interview with you sometime...

24:36.595 --> 24:38.967
concentrating on your
views on youth. I've

24:38.968 --> 24:41.133
heard a lot about them
from my son Peter.

24:41.225 --> 24:44.895
He's only 12, but your ideas have
made a big impression on him.

24:44.978 --> 24:47.064
Excuse me.

24:48.190 --> 24:50.526
The Israeli
ambassador has to go.

24:53.120 --> 24:55.770
Of course. I'd be pleased
to talk to you. Give,

24:55.771 --> 24:58.033
um, Harvey a call.
He'll arrange a time.

24:58.116 --> 25:02.412
- How about Sunday?
- Well, Sundays I usually spend with Peter.

25:02.496 --> 25:05.833
Fine. Bring Peter
along too. Excuse me.

25:26.436 --> 25:29.148
Come on, you two!
You'll get wet!

25:45.080 --> 25:47.583
Mummy, look what
Damien's given me!

25:47.666 --> 25:50.419
- No, you can't.
- He can. He just did.

25:51.420 --> 25:53.922
It's safer with him. If
I have a collision...

25:54.006 --> 25:57.634
we might have some sort of
international crisis on our hands.

25:57.718 --> 26:00.053
I'm not sure you should
spoil him so much.

26:00.137 --> 26:03.140
Well, to tell you the truth,
<i>he's</i> been spoiling <i>me.</i>

26:03.223 --> 26:06.643
It's not every day you get the
chance to be a boy again.

26:08.270 --> 26:10.355
Well...

26:10.439 --> 26:12.733
English weather.

26:13.484 --> 26:17.946
<i>- (Peter)</i> Go on, dog. Go and get it.
<i>- (Damien)</i> Tell me about Peter's father.

26:18.030 --> 26:20.407
<i>(Kate)</i> He died just
after Peter was born.

26:20.491 --> 26:24.953
- Have <i>you</i> never thought of getting married?
- No. I'm too much of a sceptic.

26:25.037 --> 26:29.374
- Oh, yes?
- Besides, I've never really had the time.

26:31.919 --> 26:35.172
Peter's always wanted
me to buy him a dog.

26:35.255 --> 26:38.342
Well, you should. Dogs and
boys go great together.

26:38.425 --> 26:41.512
We've had one of these dogs in
the family since I was a kid.

26:41.595 --> 26:45.974
- They used to march with the Roman army.
- Did they?

26:46.058 --> 26:48.560
They're as old as sin.

26:53.023 --> 26:56.401
- Feel like some lunch?
- Good idea.

26:56.485 --> 26:59.501
Probably realized my
favourite subject is

26:59.502 --> 27:02.449
me, not only because
I'm very beautiful...

27:02.533 --> 27:04.243
I am beautiful!

27:07.871 --> 27:11.124
People from all over the
world came for our actors...

27:11.208 --> 27:15.045
but where are the new ones gonna
train if we haven't got any stages?

27:15.129 --> 27:19.800
And the reason we haven't got stages is
cos people are not going to the theatre!

27:19.883 --> 27:21.802
They are watching television.

27:21.885 --> 27:24.421
You're sitting in a
bar, and at 11 o'clock

27:24.422 --> 27:27.015
they say "You have 10
minutes to drink up."

27:27.432 --> 27:32.062
You've paid a fortune for that drink
and they throw you out in the streets.

27:32.146 --> 27:35.004
"The day of Christ is
at hand" wrote St Paul

27:35.005 --> 27:37.734
in his second letter
to the Thessalonians.

27:37.818 --> 27:40.195
"Yet let no man be deceived..."

27:40.279 --> 27:44.867
for that day shall not come until
the man of sins is revealed...

27:44.950 --> 27:48.495
"the son of perdition,
the Antichrist."

27:48.579 --> 27:50.747
"And be not deceived by him...

27:50.831 --> 27:55.961
for Satan himself is transformed
into an angel of light."

27:56.044 --> 27:59.475
The hour of Christ's
Second Coming draws nigh.

27:59.476 --> 28:02.176
The prophecies
fulfilled one by one.

28:02.259 --> 28:06.972
Right now, my friends, in the
constellation of Cassiopeia...

28:07.055 --> 28:12.561
a holy trinity of stars is converging
to herald our Lord's Second Coming.

28:12.644 --> 28:17.983
"Rejoice, you heavens and you that dwell
in them" commands St John in Revelation.

28:18.066 --> 28:20.662
"But woe to you, sea and
earth, for the devil"

28:20.663 --> 28:22.863
hath come down to you
in great fury...

28:22.946 --> 28:27.743
"knowing that his time is short, and the
Prince of Darkness shall be mighty."

28:27.826 --> 28:31.079
"And he shall flourish
and destroy the mighty."

28:31.163 --> 28:35.834
"And he shall cause craft
to prosper in his hands."

28:35.918 --> 28:38.837
"And by peace shall
he destroy many!"

28:42.925 --> 28:46.595
I followed them through the crowd,
but couldn't get close enough.

28:46.678 --> 28:49.640
He was with a woman and
a boy of about 11.

28:49.723 --> 28:54.603
- Who was the woman?
- She's a television interviewer.

28:55.145 --> 28:58.649
I asked someone who went up
to her for an autograph.

28:59.107 --> 29:03.403
Kate Reynolds. She apparently
is quite some celebrity.

29:03.487 --> 29:06.031
- And the boy?
- Probably her son.

29:06.114 --> 29:10.828
Please, Father, let it be me. Let me be the
bait to flush him out and destroy him.

29:10.911 --> 29:13.747
Thorn and I have made
contact eye to eye.

29:13.748 --> 29:16.583
That is exactly why
it cannot be you.

29:17.334 --> 29:19.586
We have to strike him off guard.

29:19.670 --> 29:24.842
Yet the target must be still... for
the marksman to be sure of his aim.

29:25.843 --> 29:28.345
A sitting target...

