major part in achieving it.

31:59.371 --> 32:01.623
You have an interest
in young people.

32:01.707 --> 32:05.711
What are your plans as president of
the United Nations Youth Council?

32:05.794 --> 32:10.466
A great many things, but I think
the most important task I have...

32:10.549 --> 32:14.803
