35:06.517 --> 35:09.186
But I had the love of my
true father to protect me.

35:09.269 --> 35:11.897
You said there were seven.
Where are the other six?

35:11.980 --> 35:14.691
That's what we have to find out.

35:16.527 --> 35:21.949
Someone must have dug them up from
the old Thorn Museum in Chicago.

35:22.032 --> 35:25.369
