in man's image.

40:01.728 --> 40:05.524
But while you were born
of an impotent god...

40:06.942 --> 40:10.362
I was conceived of a jackal.

40:11.697 --> 40:15.534
Born of Satan, the
desolate one...

40:16.869 --> 40:18.954
the nail...

40:21.832 --> 40:27.921
Your pain on the cross was but a splinter
compared to the agony of my father...

40:28.005 --> 40:30.799
cast out from heaven...

40:30.883 --> 40:33.010
the fallen angel...

40:33.093 --> 40:36.138
banished, reviled...

40:40.142 --> 40:45.772
I would drive deeper the thorns
into your rancid carcass...

40:45.856 --> 40:49.109
