passed them on to a monastery in Italy.

46:40.946 --> 46:42.004
Subi...

46:42.087 --> 46:45.174
Subiaco. The monastery
of San Benedetto.

46:45.257 --> 46:48.844
Yeah, Subiaco. We've got our
people in Italy working on it.

46:48.927 --> 46:52.598
- Unless something happens, they should...
- It's too late.

46:52.681 --> 46:55.851
They're here in England for
the birth of the Nazarene.

46:56.935 --> 47:00.355
Trying to destroy me
before I destroy them.

47:04.318 --> 47:08.614
He was born last night.
I feel his presence.

47:09.031 --> 47:13.035
Like a virus, a parasite,
feeding on my energy...

47:13.118 --> 47:16.038
trying to drain me of power.

47:17.372 --> 47:20.918
For every day that he
lives and grows...

47:21.001 --> 47:23.712
my force will weaken.

47:27.007 --> 47:29.927
Hide if you must, Nazarene...

47:31.053 --> 47:33.472
but I will hunt you down.

47:42.981 --> 47:47.694
- Why is he just sitting there?
- Waiting for me to follow him.

47:47.778 --> 47:51.573
He must be an idiot if he thinks
you're gonna do something like that.

47:51.657 --> 47:54.125
He knows that's exactly
what I intend to do.

47:54.126 --> 47:56.703
But what if he's got
one of those daggers?

47:57.704 --> 48:00.457
I'll be wasting my
time if he hasn't.

49:34.259 --> 49:37.638
Matteus here. I'm
10 minutes away.

49:37.721 --> 49:41.308
Thorn's about... 500
yards behind me.

51:00.804 --> 51:02.681
