53:14.688 --> 53:18.859
Yeah, yeah. Sure. He was born 10
minutes before midnight, March 23rd.

53:18.942 --> 53:22.488
<i>(woman)</i> Whenever you're
ready, Mr. Ambassador.

53:24.156 --> 53:26.492
